    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> lentil & mushroom lasagne</strong> with the <strong>salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the<strong> balsamic dressing </strong>over the salad</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
